Triceradon walked back inside the Ark. He left his dinobots outside to stand watch, while he went inside to look for something to do. "Attension all maximal units," He said into his com, "My dinobots and I are getting bored. Is there anything we can do for anyone?" He hoped somebody would reply soon. He was really getting bored here.
